<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #4CAF50, #45a049); padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
      <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0;">Booking Confirmed!</h1>
    </div>
    <div
      style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"
    >
      <p>Hello {{menteeName}},</p>
      <p>Your mentorship session has been successfully booked! Here are your booking details:</p>

      <div style="background-color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <h2 style="color: #4CAF50; margin-top: 0;">Session Details</h2>
        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Mentor:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{mentorName}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Plan:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{planType}} - {{planDescription}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Date:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{meetingDate}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Time:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{startTime}} - {{endTime}}</td>
          </tr>
          {{#if location}}
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Location:</td>
              <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{location}}</td>
            </tr>
          {{/if}}
        </table>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <h2 style="color: #4CAF50; margin-top: 0;">Payment Summary</h2>
        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Amount Paid:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-align: right;">${{amount}}</td>
          </tr>
          {{#if discountAmount}}
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Discount Applied:</td>
              <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-align: right; color: #4CAF50;">-${{discountAmount}}</td>
            </tr>
          {{/if}}
          <tr style="border-top: 2px solid #ddd;">
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;">Total:</td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;">${{totalAmount}}</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      {{#if message}}
        <div
          style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; margin: 20px 0;"
        >
          <p style="margin: 0; color: #856404;"><strong>Your Message:</strong></p>
          <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #856404;">{{message}}</p>
        </div>
      {{/if}}

      <div
        style="background-color: #fff9e6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; margin: 20px 0;"
      >
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #e65100;"><strong>‚è≥ Meeting Status: Pending</strong></p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #e65100;">
          Your booking has been confirmed and payment received. The meeting is currently in
          <strong>pending status</strong>
          as your mentor needs to set up the Google Meet link.
          <strong>You will receive an email notification as soon as your mentor confirms the meeting and adds the link.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>üìå Important Notes:</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
          <li>Please wait for the meeting confirmation email with the Google Meet link</li>
          <li>You will be notified via email once the mentor schedules the meeting</li>
          <li>Make sure to join the session on time once you receive the meeting link</li>
          <li>If you need to reschedule, please contact your mentor in advance</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>We hope you have a productive mentorship session!</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br />Mentoria Support Team</p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #888; font-size: 0.8em;">
      <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
